{
  "stem": "24212.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the usual procedure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They cut our hair, all hair-- on your head, pubic hair, under your arms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took away everything you had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I remember clutching some photographs in my left hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't where I got them, from my purse probably.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everything taken away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No gas, shower, real shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And afterwards, we got lager clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never had a zebra.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had a gray, shirt-like dress, like a blouse, but it went to my knees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some girls got the same gray dress, no, no belt, just a button here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was, I don't know, five sizes too big.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Others got one that they could barely get into, so it was big changing around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had such gorgeous shoes, handmade, the luxury of my life at that time, handmade shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course those were gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I didn't get clogs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Most people got clogs, you know those wooden shoes, very hard to walk in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I admire these kids who, these days, it's very fashionable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But evidently they are made differently.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I never tried them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I wouldn't wear them if you gave them to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I got some miserable black high shoes, you know, to my ankle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were slightly small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "No stockings, no underwear, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we looked at each other, we didn't recognize each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then they took us to our block, which is the barracks, called them blocks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And later on, I found out that these blocks were for about 450 to 500 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were 1,450, give or take 5%.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I never counted, [LAUGHS] really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three to a [NON-ENGLISH]-- three to a cot or to a space.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So called mattresses-- so called.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
